%% 0.6: New note in Single page app diagram
%% Create a diagram depicting the situation where the user creates a new note using the single-page version of the app.

sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User writes a note and clicks Save
    Note right of browser: JavaScripts intercepts the form submission and prevents page reload
    Note right of browser: Browser creates a new note object

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: HTTP 201 Created

    Note right of browser: Browser updates the notes list and re-renders the view whithout reloading